name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: NetSuite: Saved Search and Dataset Export

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export your saved searches, datasets and workbooks to Suitescript.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
For NetSuite developers who want to export saved searches for use in their code. Supports SS1.0 and SS2.X.

From the "Edit" mode of a Saved Search in NetSuite, click the "Export as SuiteScript".

Some search types are not supported. 

Export your saved datasets and workbooks to Suitescript.

For NetSuite developers who want to export saved datasets and workbooks for use in their code.

From a saved dataset/workbook in NetSuite, click the "Export as SuiteScript". 

Please note that your saved search/dataset/workbook must be saved before it can be exported. Does not work with Templates.
